## Output

Write the complete plan to `./PLAN.md`. Overwrite any existing PLAN.md.

Structure:

```
# Plan — [Feature Name]
_Branch: `feature/short-name` | Date: YYYY-MM-DD_

## Pre-implementation checklist
...

## Tasks

### Task 1 — ...
...

### Task N — ...
...

## Post-implementation checklist
...
```

